One minute they wanna be with you and the next they act like ur some kind of disease. i got to learn today about how guys are different around their friends with their girlfriend. when i say different i mean in a bad way. not only do they treat u like dirt but they avoid u and go talk to a other girl who is just rude and might like. then when their friends are gone they act like nothing happened and go in for a hug or kiss. i think i might be jelous but im pissed like no other right now too

Even though Valentines Day is the day of love doesnt mean that u have to spend it with a guy that u r dating or that u like. i mean yeah that would be kewl but thats not what the whole damn day is about. ppl should be happy spending Valentines Day with their friends who love them and who can give them everything that a guy or girl can and more besides affection unless they swing that way. I hate how every one turned V-Day into this whole big thing just cuz they arent with some one. besides if ur not with some one then u dont have to worry about getting them ne thing which saves u a lot of stress and u wont have to worry about getting ur heart broke. i thought V-Day would be fun but its only the 13 and i have spent a whole day hearing ppl b**** about it.

For a different topic i hate people that go and tell other ppl ur secrets after they sware that they arent going to tell ne one especially one of their best friends. i mean there are certain things that arent meant to be spread around and that u can only trust with a few ppl. if this perosn had a lj then i would hope that they read this.Now that I got all my anger out I feel a little better

 

Any ways I love everyone and I hope u have a great Valentines Day!!!!!!!

 

<3 always Brittany
